description:
This is a 44 minute workout called '40 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT || Intermediate Pilates Class' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Hope you enjoy this new 40 Minute Full Body Pilates Workout! This Intermediate Pilates class will strengthen the entire body, with an extra emphasis on our legs and core!
